question_details.fine_print:
This question will resolve based on the release date of the specific recording that tops the charts. It is immaterial whether a different version of the single was recorded and released previously.&#x20;

For example in 2004, this question would have resolved as 2000s because that year's Christmas number one: Band Aid 20's version of "Do They Know It's Christmas?," was released in 2004, even though the original "Do They Know It's Christmas?" was recorded and released in 1984.

Each decade will be defined by the first three digits of the year. For example, any recording released between January 1, 1990, and December 31, 1999, will be considered a 1990s release.

